import {Input,FieldHolder, FormHolder, Button} from "../style"
const Login = () =>{
    return <FormHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
                <Input type={"text"} name="email" placeholder="Email" width={"100%"}/>
        </FieldHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
            <Input type={"password"} name="password" placeholder="Password" width={"100%"}/>
        </FieldHolder>
        <FieldHolder>
            <Button name="button" value="Button" width={"max-content"}>Login</Button>
        </FieldHolder>
    </FormHolder>
}
export default Login
